extendedInfo.description: ** Note this app IS NOT A STANDALONE! This skin requires GO Keyboard (Free on Market) or Ultra KeyboardMatch your keyboard with* Rose Dark Phone GO SMS Theme: http://bit.ly/HqLFBtFeatures* Optional custom font (see below to activate font)* Beautifully rendered graphics* Unique glow effect on letters* Activate through GO Keyboard settings!Install* Select done, return to GO Keyboard's Settings (hold 123 on Keyboard), and select the Rose Dark Phone skin from the list of available skins.Activate the font* Go into GO Keyboard Settings, Advanced Setting, Font setting, Scan fonts. Once finished, select DarkPhone [Rose Dark Phone GO Keyboard]Enjoy!* If you don't love it within the first fifteen minutes, return it! If you do, let us know in the comments!Have questions?** As we are unable to respond to comments, feel free to get in touch with us through email, Facebook and TwitterFollow us for our latest themes!* Twitter (@aBbtdesigns): http://bit.ly/xqfEl1* Facebook (aBbtdesigns): http://on.fb.me/yO5ULmaBbtKeywords: hot, dark, colorful, black
